<codeline><highlight class="normal">constexpr<sp/>uint32_t<sp/>LAYER_ENEMY<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>=<sp/>1<sp/>&lt;&lt;<sp/>1;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">constexpr<sp/>uint32_t<sp/>LAYER_POWER_UP<sp/>=<sp/>1<sp/>&lt;&lt;<sp/>2;</highlight></codeline>
